03:36.834 --> 03:38.634
Shit.

03:41.338 --> 03:42.746
What?

03:42.748 --> 03:44.840
There were
three cans of gas.

04:02.768 --> 04:05.286
Battery's probably dead.

04:06.772 --> 04:08.681
Hey.

04:10.418 --> 04:13.035
Look, even if you got
some of that gas in there,

04:13.037 --> 04:14.319
it's not
gonna start.

04:14.321 --> 04:15.537
- Back away.
- It's alright.

04:15.539 --> 04:17.873
We just need
the gas back.

04:17.875 --> 04:19.358
- "We"?
- Easy there.

04:19.360 --> 04:20.801
I said back away.

04:20.803 --> 04:22.118
No,
she's right.

04:22.120 --> 04:23.696
We do need it.
So listen.

04:23.698 --> 04:25.288
Why don't we
talk about it?

04:25.290 --> 04:26.640
Just get the hell
away from me.

04:27.960 --> 04:31.896
Hey, need you
to lower the knife.

04:33.557 --> 04:35.816
Come on.

04:35.818 --> 04:37.276
Lower the knife.

04:49.056 --> 04:51.481
Now, why don't you tell us
where you're trying to get.

04:53.911 --> 04:55.318
Morgan.

04:56.655 --> 04:59.248
No. No.

04:59.250 --> 05:01.008
They found me.

05:05.089 --> 05:07.406
Get in the van.
Al.

05:15.191 --> 05:17.933
Shh-shh-shh.

05:43.219 --> 05:45.869
Al.

05:45.871 --> 05:47.388
Four?

05:53.971 --> 05:56.880
- Shit.
- What?

05:56.882 --> 05:59.474
- Uh, gas cap.
- Al.

06:45.430 --> 06:48.132
Over here!

06:48.134 --> 06:50.600
He went this way!

07:00.855 --> 07:02.496
Okay,
start talking.

07:04.449 --> 07:05.633
Who the hell
was that?

07:05.635 --> 07:07.776
It's alright.

07:07.778 --> 07:09.470
We can help you.

07:12.716 --> 07:15.550
That's what they said.

07:28.186 --> 07:30.447
Subtitles by explosiveskull
